Class HeaderInitialValue

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ed.csbe.sbsivisual.sbsiDataFormat.HeaderInitialValue

public class HeaderInitialValue
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates an Initial Value data element of the header file.
Instances of this class are immutable once created. Equality is based on the String value of speciesName value

Author:
Richard Adams
